sketch.compiler.passes.printers

Class CodePrinterVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FEReplacer
      • sketch.compiler.passes.lowering.SymbolTableVisitor
        • sketch.compiler.passes.printers.CodePrinterVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PromelaCodePrinter

    public class CodePrinterVisitor
extends SymbolTableVisitor
    A parent class for code printers that strictly adhere to the visitor pattern. Use the CodePrinter class if the strict visitor pattern is too awkward for your needs. This default CodePrinterVisitor prints the code using a C/Java-like syntax.
    Author:
    Chris Jones
    See Also:
    CodePrinter
